---
import TemplateLayout from "@/templates/law-prestige/TemplateLayout.astro";
---

<TemplateLayout
  title="Industries We Serve | Prestige Law"
  description="From private equity to global conglomerates — the sectors and client profiles Prestige Law is built to defend."
  active="industries"
  canonicalPath="/templates/law-prestige/industries"
>
<main>
<!-- Hero Section -->
<section class="relative py-stack-lg overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-lowest">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-gutter items-center">
<div class="z-10">
<span class="font-label-md text-secondary uppercase tracking-[0.3em] block mb-4">Elite Sector Focus</span>
<h1 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg mb-8 leading-[1.05]">Advocates for the <br/><span class="italic font-normal">Global Elite.</span></h1>
<p class="font-body-lg text-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-xl mb-12">
                        Prestige Litigation provides bespoke legal defense and strategic advocacy for the world's most significant institutional and private interests. We navigate multi-jurisdictional complexities with a razor-sharp focus on asset preservation and reputational integrity.
                    </p>
<div class="flex gap-6">
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-10 py-4 font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest hover:bg-secondary transition-all">
                            View Credentials
                        </button>
</div>
</div>
<div class="relative h-[600px] hidden lg:block">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center grayscale shadow-2xl z-0" data-alt="A high-contrast black and white photograph of a sleek, modern architectural structure with sharp angles and dramatic shadows. The image captures the essence of quiet wealth and structural integrity, reflecting a sophisticated and authoritative atmosphere. Bright daylight creates deep slate shadows against pearl white concrete surfaces." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuC-EN-SbskXKWbfUNvsevyyAkBheIo8GWpBICQrSeamw4n73mQ1m6hIKOe8HPhNypD55Nngum3slG0lWnJ_2wIVvI5cUXhDHDkhiXR5zUeB9Jqc-OErWUt9Cz2tB-IUUwS_uLYg_0NYLLvUR9nO7RgIWzLbp62TqfKovz21U3t2JG7ogHgJma6eW_6yBLzvgDqEL5RCux2Peam4dXJy5y_hCYmunEnO3Kxco7x4P_abZlsWzhiqknW3um4P_7L3KJS2MD_XxHGbONST')"></div>
<div class="absolute -bottom-10 -left-10 bg-primary text-on-primary p-12 max-w-xs deep-shadow">
<span class="text-display-lg font-display-lg block mb-2">$50B+</span>
<p class="font-lp-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest opacity-80">Assets currently under litigation management</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Industries Grid -->
<section class="py-stack-lg">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="mb-24 flex justify-between items-end border-b border-outline/10 pb-8">
<div>
<h2 class="font-lp-headline-md text-lp-headline-md mb-2">Our Domains</h2>
<p class="font-body-md text-on-surface-variant">Specialized units for high-stakes environments.</p>
</div>
<span class="font-lp-label-sm text-outline uppercase tracking-tighter">Scroll to Explore</span>
</div>
<div class="space-y-stack-lg">
<!-- 1. Fortune 500 -->
<div class="reveal-up grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter group items-start">
<div class="md:col-span-5 h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center grayscale group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="A minimalist, high-contrast black and white photograph of a prestigious corporate headquarters facade. The lighting is sharp, emphasizing the vertical glass and steel lines. The mood is powerful, professional, and reflects the immense scale of a Fortune 500 enterprise in a metropolitan setting." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCeZ2SAliwgBiA-_CmAYUV8zSMudeyvsu6QkJ3yhwUXbEmTs9m3KpkM7BhOzXp2dIPEdljos_t3_dipfd9rHq2YCSlfkhZZz3inxc9Pl_zX20uso_ZFYODoNUY-PcHbrsyOTI_-leurVOVaPcnQiL9bmOJmw288A9qYUmc273kfWKhy77pHbB7ApDtTAkTZRxJCQGCeAE-GgAavF4IMipiXMkjPVwmHpiI-2aaUnZu9gNBKquGb7osAa_IbY1OHb6IlyYKDk9VoezVu')"></div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center h-full md:pl-12 py-8">
<span class="font-lp-label-sm text-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Sector 01</span>
<h3 class="font-display-lg text-[40px] mb-6">Fortune 500 Enterprises</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                                Defensive strategies against class actions, regulatory scrutiny, and competitive sabotage. We serve as global counsel for entities whose operations span across seventy-plus jurisdictions.
                            </p>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-low border-l-4 border-primary">
<span class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase block mb-2 tracking-widest">Case Narrative</span>
<p class="font-body-md italic text-on-surface">"Successfully defended a multi-national conglomerate against a $1.2B anti-trust suit, securing a full dismissal in record time through aggressive pre-trial motions."</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 2. Private Equity -->
<div class="reveal-up grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter group items-start flex-row-reverse">
<div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center h-full md:pr-12 py-8 md:text-right md:items-end order-2 md:order-1">
<span class="font-lp-label-sm text-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Sector 02</span>
<h3 class="font-display-lg text-[40px] mb-6">Private Equity Firms</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                                Precision litigation during restructuring, buyouts, and portfolio disputes. Our team specializes in the complex fiduciary duties inherent in high-value asset management.
                            </p>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-low border-r-4 border-primary text-right">
<span class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase block mb-2 tracking-widest">Case Narrative</span>
<p class="font-body-md italic text-on-surface">"Mitigated post-acquisition liability for a tier-one PE firm, preserving $850M in projected returns through tactical settlement negotiations."</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5 h-[400px] overflow-hidden order-1 md:order-2">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center grayscale group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="Close-up architectural detail of a high-end boardroom with charcoal leather and polished dark wood. High-contrast lighting highlights the refined textures and sharp corners. Minimalist and luxurious aesthetic suitable for a private equity setting." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuCUpGqWNMEcLmxCWFpaEQmitLHzuLAgn6Nlda6L7oEYvwlM3rp2wZ59AYjZuA_qAPe3yRKelO4dRjIkgkEF0EQ2nMltMJraWKfID2kcbnB4i_g62nJ4VqEEKJvhyGThocXWXenyIAdIaLEtvXpVxipXXeqUwjqPwwL8oMIW2o-oSNDXRkLaQSxTllgoyUZsvbNPSHJsVbsqjuO3YIw_Bv2lQGTO1cnbvxctSJsiOrAmcuMejhW76EDrTqdBJLoW1KjYwHKQh87V1Sxc')"></div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 3. Family Offices -->
<div class="reveal-up grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter group items-start">
<div class="md:col-span-5 h-[400px] overflow-hidden">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center grayscale group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="A serene yet authoritative black and white interior of a private library or study. Large windows cast long, dramatic shadows across minimalist furniture. The mood is one of quiet, multi-generational wealth and absolute privacy." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuD3WPSnWo9Rl91savJdXE6ZO2FmX3cS-l-_KwDuYH1l99yCy2IToN7Er6qiKBV5WSwLhONRsHamXhm5urbtIebviRseMT8GMzBT3Y_H2gW8bZiHAOW3imsRvLoo-Nf2sAlbq1gIbUOnda3AN870asvDKBfZUcQKv02nl4908oygMcOG2B8Hgu92nyad1aNGmL6h7eCArMxBApVp1YRmZmtEIEv4DYTZTv0Ma3tYY5w4WDkaWsKdH7q5Xob3kSOPCiIBOpMt8o-kbNv3')"></div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center h-full md:pl-12 py-8">
<span class="font-lp-label-sm text-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Sector 03</span>
<h3 class="font-display-lg text-[40px] mb-6">Family Offices</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                                Safeguarding the legacy of the world’s ultra-high-net-worth families. We handle inter-generational disputes, estate litigation, and philanthropic governance with absolute discretion.
                            </p>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-low border-l-4 border-primary">
<span class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase block mb-2 tracking-widest">Case Narrative</span>
<p class="font-body-md italic text-on-surface">"Resolved a high-profile multi-jurisdictional inheritance conflict involving assets across the Cayman Islands, Switzerland, and London, ensuring total privacy."</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<!-- 4. Tech Conglomerates -->
<div class="reveal-up grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-12 gap-gutter group items-start flex-row-reverse">
<div class="md:col-span-7 flex flex-col justify-center h-full md:pr-12 py-8 md:text-right md:items-end order-2 md:order-1">
<span class="font-lp-label-sm text-secondary mb-4 uppercase tracking-[0.2em]">Sector 04</span>
<h3 class="font-display-lg text-[40px] mb-6">Tech Conglomerates</h3>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant mb-8 max-w-2xl">
                                Protecting intellectual property and dominance in the digital frontier. Our tech litigation unit bridges the gap between complex software engineering and international legal frameworks.
                            </p>
<div class="p-8 bg-surface-container-low border-r-4 border-primary text-right">
<span class="font-label-md text-primary uppercase block mb-2 tracking-widest">Case Narrative</span>
<p class="font-body-md italic text-on-surface">"Enforced global patent rights for a Silicon Valley giant, resulting in the largest licensing settlement in the history of telecommunications."</p>
</div>
</div>
<div class="md:col-span-5 h-[400px] overflow-hidden order-1 md:order-2">
<div class="w-full h-full bg-cover bg-center grayscale group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-700" data-alt="Futuristic architectural elements of a data center or tech hub, captured in sharp black and white. Repetitive geometric patterns and glowing lines create a sense of advanced technology and high-stakes infrastructure." style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBeFLorxrjLA0CaIBzQNrya0hi1QF7I5h_d9Rm4QMsez7LGJxTkPgMnqoHbgbFSSETQYzrIWwunNo4vzoviINh1yZ51PV5kglUYIFTLsfgsdgDeW_t3FpYdhtUjfQLFd0n9LA65mqiDW_HAWKVNb7kX8c9sZJnU44KNAGsQCyvTp57NXWPfYVVUIcdiFaZqJRo6_jdvh9roDdojgojpBmUoQEd_MuEXjxE1ZCKa3Al7zKzXMoMvpr2KEUUn_PutfreAQtKsei6lNXzl')"></div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- Global Reach Map Area -->
<section class="bg-primary text-on-primary py-stack-lg">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop">
<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-gutter">
<div class="lg:col-span-1">
<h2 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg mb-6">Jurisdictional Mastery.</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg opacity-70 mb-12">Litigation capacity in every major financial center. Our reach is global; our focus is singular.</p>
<div class="space-y-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4 border-b border-on-primary/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest">London</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4 border-b border-on-primary/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest">Geneva</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4 border-b border-on-primary/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest">Singapore</span>
</div>
<div class="flex items-center gap-4 py-4 border-b border-on-primary/10">
<span class="material-symbols-outlined text-secondary">location_on</span>
<span class="font-label-md uppercase tracking-widest">New York</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="lg:col-span-2 min-h-[500px] bg-primary-container relative group overflow-hidden">
<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center opacity-40 group-hover:scale-105 transition-transform duration-[2s]" data-alt="A stylized, dark monochromatic map showing global connections and financial hubs. The map is minimalist with subtle glows on key cities. High-contrast and professional, suitable for a global legal firm's presence." data-location="London" style="background-image: url('https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuDizwX_-gYxM8-RayMah99VC26YkYy0B8R2_YiMNUpAbhWTY7DTXQDLM8S_PZ_Ytnj0L3HE99P1zV9OkKimyoBPCZZEGT7C3BfGMTBmQ3RbxK1hYHgLRi73oFnX30RSx5-5paPrjMv9rTtQL0loSaBeRKfW8RPTarhbPR3_F0pMzoWePSlCu3-LcHzO8PUrANSs5H1E4TRQk0Vw4GFz5SqzDeKcabVPPPrENMjlordm_DssYwrtfw22cszzuKRFILwJ7qf4492DsrdY')"></div>
<div class="absolute inset-0 flex items-center justify-center">
<div class="text-center p-12 bg-primary/80 backdrop-blur-md border border-on-primary/10">
<p class="font-headline-sm mb-4">"Boundaries do not limit our influence."</p>
<span class="font-lp-label-sm uppercase tracking-widest text-secondary">Global Managing Partner</span>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</section>
<!-- CTA -->
<section class="py-stack-lg bg-surface-container">
<div class="max-w-lp-container-max mx-auto px-margin-desktop text-center">
<h2 class="font-display-lg text-display-lg mb-8">Secure Your Position.</h2>
<p class="font-body-lg text-on-surface-variant max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-12">
                    Our intake process is as rigorous as our advocacy. We exclusively represent clients whose legal challenges require the highest tier of strategic litigation.
                </p>
<button class="bg-primary text-on-primary px-16 py-5 font-label-md uppercase tracking-[0.3em] hover:bg-secondary transition-all deep-shadow">
                    Request Formal Inquiry
                </button>
</div>
</section>
</main>

</TemplateLayout>
